      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个工业物联网的投票部署流程图。场景是：Voter1作为外部参与者，要通过swaparoo部署器启动一个MQTT Broker实例，然后委员会节点返回边缘节点的访问凭证。整个流程涉及Zoe合约框架作为中间层。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Voter1",
        "swaparoo<brdeployer",
        "Zoe",
        "swaparoo<brcommittee",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我梳理一下：Voter1是actor角色，Core代表swaparoo部署器，然后Zoe是独立的participant，委员会也是swaparoo下的committee节点。启动顺序是Core先调用Zoe的startInstance，然后Zoe转发给委员会，委员会返回EdgeNode给Zoe，Zoe再包装成PLC Logic返回给Core？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Zoe",
        "Ctee",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，但PLC Logic那个返回是Zoe给Core的，不是委员会直接给的。然后Core还要向委员会索取投票邀请凭证，委员会返回的是ActuatorController的权限列表，最后Core把invitationV1发给Voter1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Ctee",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "invitationV1",
        "V1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先画出主体结构和前四步消息：V1作为actor，Core、Zoe、Ctee三个participant，标注好swaparoo的部署器和委员会身份。然后画Core到Zoe的startInstance调用，Zoe到Ctee的start转发，Ctee返回EdgeNode，Zoe再返回PLC Logic给Core。",
      "elements_involved": [
