    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下语法：Core到Ctee的消息写成E(IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode).getVoterInvitations(IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker)对吗？意思是边缘节点实例调用获取邀请方法，参数是Broker标识。",
